ABOUT

Hi, I am Agnese Kalmane. I study 3D Media Design & Management in University / Hochschule Fresenius in Wiesbaden. I am currently in 3. Semester. I am very creative and talented and also speak 4 Languages - Russian, English, German and Latvian fluently. Experience: Interaction Design, Communications Design, Storytelling & Dramaturgy, Motion Design, Imaging Design, Design Thinking, Project Management and Marketing.

Programs that I am very good at: Cinema 4D, Sony Vegas, Adobe Creative Cloud - Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign. I know how to use Adobe After Effects and Adobe Premiere Pro. (Advanced level) I can take photos and edit them, and fly drone when needed.
